100,000元以下罰\r\n金；致重傷者，處3年以下有期徒刑、拘役或300,000元以下罰金\r\n。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e6%98%93%2c634%2c20220812%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,交易,634,20220812,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交易","JNO":"634","JDATE":"20220812","JTITLE":"過失致重傷害"}